:

1. *Trebaš* da kupiš nove cipele. (You need to buy new shoes.)
2. Gde trebaš da odeš? (Where do you need to go?)
3. Šta ti *trebaš*? (What do you need?)
4. *Trebaš* da se setiš da stigneš na vreme. (You need to remember to arrive on time.)
5. *Trebaš* da obnoviš svoju vozačku dozvolu. (You need to renew your driver's license.)
6. *Trebaš* da izabereš jednu stvar. (You need to choose one thing.)
7. Da li znaš šta *trebaš* da uradiš? (Do you know what you need to do?)
8. *Trebaš* da se spremiš za put. (You need to get ready for the trip.)